.devlyn/criteria.generated.md-9-- [ ] Load processing fee percent, fixed fee cents, dispute fee cents, reserve percent, and minimum payout threshold cents from `data/payout-rules.json` at runtime — never hardcoded; a rules-file edit alone must change output.
